ac.ucy.cs.spdx.compatibility

Class SPDXCompatibilityError

  • java.lang.Object
    • ac.ucy.cs.spdx.compatibility.SPDXCompatibilityError

  • public class SPDXCompatibilityError
extends java.lang.Object
    This is SPDX Compatibility Error class. It is based on the results of areCompatible() method of SPDXCompatibility class and provides info on whether the .rdf files are compatible and if not it gives the error message and possible solutions on it.
    Author:
    dpasch01
